data.description:
Custom mountain living home on 10.54 Acres, bordering National Forest. 2,788 SqFt. Living room offers large south facing window's with stunning views, pellet stove, vaulted ceilings/great room. Newer kitchen appliances all included. Washer and dryer included in-between the kitchen and oversized 2 car garage. Walk-Out to Large wrap around deck with picnic table from the dining and living. Upper level has a large Master with 5 Piece bath, and walk in closet. Two more additional bedrooms in the upper with another full bath. Walk out lower level family room, with wood burning stove. Lots of great hiking, right out of your backyard. Horses allowed property with 60x70 Morton Building Barn for additional. The mountain air is clean, crisp with beautiful trees and beautiful Mountain View's! 
House will be completely empty of personal property in pictures.
Inside of house is being completely freshly painted!
There are 3 additional cabins on the property with a dedicated security gun vault room.
